Interface PathCore<P extends PathCore<P>>

  • Type Parameters:

    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ImmutableListPathCore

    public interface PathCore<P extends PathCore<P>>
extends Comparable<P>
    Defines basic functionality common to Path-like objects. Implementations of this class may be used to create real path objects through composition.
